* Identify & Resolve\nResource Bottlenecks
** Memory Pressure
***_ High memory utilization
***_ Spill to disk indicators
***_ Fix: larger instance size
***_ Fix: reduce partition count
***_ Fix: optimize transformations
** CPU Constraints
***_ High CPU utilization
***_ Long task execution
***_ Enable Photon acceleration
***_ Scale out workers
** Network Bottlenecks
***_ High shuffle read/write
***_ Slow execution
***_ Filter data early
***_ Use broadcast joins
***_ Repartition for colocation
** Server Load Distribution
***_ Compute Metrics tab
***_ Red = heavily loaded
***_ Blue = idle
***_ Red driver + Blue workers
***_ → Driver needs larger instance
@endmindmap
